Subject: Antenna mounting instructions

I found the 1980 sales receipt for my bus and along with it I found the
mounting instructions for the this style antenna:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/MoreParts6/241-Antenna.jpg

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/AntennaTemplate.gif

The image is 1:1 scale at 72 dpi. In other words, the distance between the
center of the two holes is exactly 38mm.

I hope it's of use to someone.

